emuInput.TitMainTitle: Group portrait, clockwise: Mr. and Mrs. Luvernis Lee, Lucille Stewart, Mrs. Harry G. Washington, Mrs. Linn Washington at banquet table, with Miriam Sharpe Fountain seated, and Wendell Freeland standing in background, in Villa Monaco during FROGS week cocktail party
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 3, 1957, pg. 12 reads: "The Frogs Entertain - The above pictures were taken at the Frogs' first affair during the club's 47th annual celebration of Frogs Week. Held Sunday at the Villa Monaco, members of the club entertained their wives and their out-of-town guests at a swank cocktail party and buffet supper...Lower photo, clock-wise: Luvernis Lee, Mrs. Lee, Miss Lucille Stewart of New York, house guest of Mrs. Linn Washington (far right), and Mrs. Harry G. Washington. - Harris Photos."
